title: The Artie Quitter Podcast FEB 25 2016 Thu.mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Regular Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Geno Bisconte, Sue Costello, Chris Cotton, Stacey Prussman & Mike Bocchetti, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.


TODAY's SHOW  (01:12:11)

Episode 213.
Artie & Dan Falato are joined by RICHARD ROEPER.




For those that didn't check the comments of the last ep posted, Artie was off for the week. They did however post this, whether it's totally new content that I'm not sure of but it is labeled as ep 213 so here it is. Hopefully Artie will be back Monday, if not check the comments of the last show posted for updates about why the next ep hasn't been posted.

Take Care & Don't Forget To Wash Your Undercarriage
